data.description: Tastefully updated 2-bedroom condo! This ground level home showcases modern wood laminate flooring complemented by ample closet space and storage solutions. The open living/dining space is complete with a cozy wood-burning fireplace. The kitchen is equipped with black and stainless steel appliances, abundant cabinetry, and a breakfast bar. Continue down the hall and discover two generously-sized bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a convenient laundry closet. A quaint back patio beckons for leisurely mornings with your favorite beverage. Completing this move-in-ready home is a detached 1-car garage. Enjoy close proximity to the community pool and relish in the amenities of a clubhouse, tennis courts, and lush greenery. Accessibility remains unrivaled with seamless connections to I-25 and I-36, ensuring effortless commuting. Indulge in retail therapy at nearby shopping destinations, or tee off at Legacy Ridge Golf Course, all just moments away. The neighborhood also offers bike paths, tranquil ponds, and sprawling parks. Welcome home!
